msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/name"
msgid "Pegasus Bridge"
msgstr "Puente Pegasus"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/name_big"
msgid "Pegasus Bridge"
msgstr "Puente Pegasus"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Victory is ours, you have done an outstanding job. This will show Jerry what "
"we’re capable of. The invasion beaches will not be threatened by flanking "
"attacks!"
msgstr ""
"La victoria es nuestra, habéis hecho un trabajo excepcional. Esto le "
"demostrará a los boches de lo que somos capaces. ¡Las playas de invasión no "
"se verán amenazadas por ataques por el flanco!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Alas there is no success to be reported. The invasion beaches will be "
"vulnerable to counterattacks as a result, and there is little we can do to "
"prevent that. We must try again immediately!"
msgstr ""
"Por desgracia, no hay ningún éxito que comunicar. Como resultado, las playas "
"de invasión serán vulnerables a los contraataques, y poco podemos hacer para "
"evitarlo. ¡Debemos volver a intentarlo inmediatamente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/date"
msgid "June 6th, 1944 · Normandy, France"
msgstr "6 de junio de 1944. Normandía, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/place"
msgid "6th Airlanding Brigade"
msgstr "6.ª Brigada Aerotransportada"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/story"
msgid ""
"To protect the invasion against German flanking attacks, a couple of bridges "
"East of the beaches must be secured. This task has been assigned to the "
"British 6th Airborne Brigade. They are to seize the bridge over the Caen "
"canal and the nearby bridge over the Orne river. \n"
"\n"
"Months of training proved to be invaluable as the pilot landed the glider "
"right at the bridge over the Orne canal. Time to spring into action! First, "
"chase the Germans out and secure Bénouville Bridge."
msgstr ""
"Para proteger la invasión contra los ataques alemanes por los flancos, hay "
"que asegurar un par de puentes al este de las playas. Esta tarea se ha "
"asignado a la 6.ª Brigada Aerotransportada británica. Deben tomar el puente "
"sobre el canal de Caen y el puente cercano sobre el río Orne. \n"
"\n"
"Los meses de entrenamiento resultaron ser muy valiosos, ya que el piloto "
"aterrizó el planeador justo en el puente sobre el canal del Orne. ¡Es hora "
"de pasar a la acción! Primero, expulsad a los alemanes y asegurad el puente "
"de Bénouville."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/gameover/defense"
msgid "You could not hold your positions."
msgstr "No pudisteis mantener vuestras posiciones."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/gameover/pl_dead"
msgid "You lost all of your units."
msgstr "Has perdido todas tus unidades."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/landing_01"
msgid ""
"The pilots almost got us killed faster than Jerry could! Is everyone "
"alright? Get your stuff and get out."
msgstr ""
"¡Los pilotos casi nos matan más rápido que Jerry! ¿Están todos bien? Recojan "
"sus cosas y salgan de aquí."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/landing_02"
msgid ""
"This bridge is what it’s all about. We have to capture and hold it until our "
"reinforcements arrive."
msgstr ""
"Este puente es lo más importante. Tenemos que capturarlo y mantenerlo hasta "
"que lleguen nuestros refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/landing_03"
msgid "Thank God Jerry didn't hear us landing. Let's keep it that way."
msgstr "Gracias a Dios Jerry no nos oyó aterrizar. Que siga siendo así."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/landing_04"
msgid ""
"Sir, there's a pillbox up ahead. Could be a right pain. Best knock it out "
"first."
msgstr ""
"Señor, hay un fortín más adelante. Podría ser un verdadero problema. Será "
"mejor que lo eliminemos primero."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/landing_05"
msgid ""
"Right, here's the plan: my section will take up positions overlooking the "
"pillbox and provide covering fire, so your men can approach the bridge."
msgstr ""
"Bien, este es el plan: mi sección tomará posiciones con vista al fortín y "
"proporcionará fuego de cobertura, para que tus hombres puedan acercarse al "
"puente."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_ally_on_position"
msgid "We're in place and ready to pin that pillbox down. Say the word."
msgstr ""
"Estamos en posición y listos para reducir ese fortín. Solo tienes que dar la "
"orden."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_player_spotted"
msgid "We’ve been spotted! Everyone, open fire!"
msgstr "¡Nos han descubierto! ¡Todos, abran fuego!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_shots_fired"
msgid "Why didn’t you wait for us?! Return fire!"
msgstr "¿Por qué no nos esperasteis? ¡Responded al fuego!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_bunker_suppressed"
msgid "Brilliant work! That pillbox is quiet."
msgstr "¡Excelente trabajo! Esa pastillera es muy silenciosa."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_pl_see_mgun"
msgid ""
"There’s an MG on the other side! Someone take it out so we can cross the "
"canal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hay un MG al otro lado! ¡Que alguien lo saque para que podamos cruzar el "
"canal!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_enemy_retreat"
msgid "Look at ‘em legging it! Not a bad start to the morning, ha?"
msgstr "¡Mira cómo corren! No está mal para empezar la mañana, ¿no?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_kwk_crew_killed"
msgid "Smart move out there. One less headache to worry about."
msgstr ""
"Una decisión inteligente. Un dolor de cabeza menos del que preocuparse."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part01_bridge_cleared"
msgid "The bridge is ours. Keep focused, I’m sure there will be more of them."
msgstr ""
"El puente es nuestro. Mantén la concentración, estoy seguro de que vendrán "
"más."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_01"
msgid ""
"It seems like Jerry hasn’t rigged the bridge with explosives, I’d wager they "
"have them stashed somewhere nearby. Let’s have a look around."
msgstr ""
"Parece que Jerry no ha colocado explosivos en el puente, apostaría a que los "
"tienen escondidos en algún lugar cercano. Echemos un vistazo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_02"
msgid "Look, some lads from the other landing zone have arrived."
msgstr "Mira, han llegado algunos chicos de la otra zona de aterrizaje."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_03"
msgid "One PIAT? That’s it? Are they having a laugh?!"
msgstr "¿Un PIAT? ¿Eso es todo? ¿Están bromeando?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_04"
msgid "I can tell them to turn around if you wish, Lieutenant."
msgstr "Puedo decirles que den la vuelta si lo deseas, teniente."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_05"
msgid ""
"I reckon it’s better than nothing. Still, this guy better treat that PIAT "
"like it’s his firstborn."
msgstr ""
"Creo que es mejor que nada. Aun así, este tipo debería tratar ese PIAT como "
"si fuera tu primogénito."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part02_06"
msgid ""
"Looks like that's the last of them. The bridge is clear, area secure, and "
"Jerry is running away. Well done! Now back to the bridge. Squad leader’s "
"meeting in 10."
msgstr ""
"Parece que ese es el último. El puente está despejado, la zona es segura y "
"Jerry está huyendo. ¡Bien hecho! Ahora regresa al puente. Reunión de jefes "
"de escuadrón en 10 minutos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/hint_civilians_01"
msgid ""
"Let’s see if there are some locals around, they might know where Jerry keeps "
"his ammo."
msgstr ""
"Veamos si hay algún lugareño por aquí, quizá sepan dónde guarda Jerry sus "
"municiones."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/pl_see_hotel_mgun"
msgid "MG! Hotel building, second floor, get to cover!"
msgstr "¡MG! Edificio del hotel, segundo piso, ¡ponte a cubierto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/flak38_see"
msgid ""
"Heads up, anti-air spotted in the field! Knock it out so our boys in the sky "
"can breathe easy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Atención, se ha detectado fuego antiaéreo en el campo! ¡Acabad con él para "
"que nuestros muchachos en el cielo puedan respirar tranquilos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/flak38_hint_destroy"
msgid ""
"We need to take out that Flak. Use a PIAT or find some explosives. Anything "
"that we can use to disable it."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que eliminar ese cañón antiaéreo. Usad un PIAT o buscad explosivos. "
"Cualquier cosa que podamos usar para inutilizarlo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/flak38_destroyed"
msgid "Nice one! That bloody Flak won't bother anyone again!"
msgstr "¡Bien hecho! ¡Ese maldito Flak no volverá a molestar a nadie!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/fake_explosives_01"
msgid "Check this out! I reckon these are the explosives meant for the bridge."
msgstr "¡Mira esto! Creo que estos son los explosivos destinados al puente."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/fake_explosives_02"
msgid "Not the charges... But have a look, perhaps we’ll find something handy."
msgstr ""
"No son las cargas explosivas... Pero échale un vistazo, quizá encontremos "
"algo útil."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/explosives_found"
msgid ""
"Here they are! Take care of those charges. One hand grenade near the vehicle "
"might be enough to blow it up."
msgstr ""
"¡Aquí están! Encárgate de esas cargas. Una granada de mano cerca del "
"vehículo podría ser suficiente para hacerlo explotar."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/explosives_destroyed"
msgid "Blimey, were they planning to blow up half of Normandy or what?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Caramba! ¿Acaso planeaban volar por los aires la mitad de Normandía o qué?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_01"
msgid ""
"Excusez-moi, monsieur... Seen any Allemania explosives? Satchels, grenades, "
"that sort?"
msgstr ""
"Disculpa, señor... ¿Has visto algún explosivo de Allemania? ¿Mochilas, "
"granadas, ese tipo de cosas?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_02"
msgid ""
"(French) No, no, monsieur, there must be some mistake. I am not sheltering "
"enemies of the Reich."
msgstr ""
"No, no, señor, debe haber algún error. Yo no estoy dando cobijo a enemigos "
"del Reich."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_03"
msgid ""
"Nah, mate, we're British! Tea, football, England! Aight, look... Explosives, "
"Boche ammunition! We need that sort of a thing, you get it?"
msgstr ""
"¡No, amigo, somos británicos! ¡Té, fútbol, Inglaterra! Vale, mira... "
"¡Explosivos, munición alemana! Necesitamos ese tipo de cosas, ¿lo entiendes?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_04"
msgid ""
"Ah, oui, oui, of course! Here small depot, but les Boches, they take it "
"away. Dominique, mon voisin, he is résistant, watch the depot, oui? Now he "
"is in the stable… Eh… West… Big box! Box en bois, comprendre? Wood box! He "
"have eyes like un faucon and moustache… Long, very long, jusqu’à Marseille! "
"Good luck, les Anglais, merci!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, oui, oui, ¡por supuesto! Aquí hay un pequeño depósito, pero los Boches "
"se lo llevan. Dominique, mon voisin, él es résistant, vigila el depósito, "
"¿oui? Ahora está en el establo... Eh... Oeste... ¡Caja grande! Caja en bois, "
"¿comprendre? ¡Caja de madera! Tiene ojos como un faucon y bigote... Largo, "
"muy largo, ¡jusqu'à Marseille! Buena suerte, les Anglais, merci!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_05"
msgid "Alright then... Got it. Thank you, monsieur. And stay safe out there."
msgstr "Muy bien, entonces... Entendido. Gracias, señor. Y cuídate ahí fuera."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/hint_civilians_02"
msgid ""
"Reckon he means the barn west of here. There is another civvie. Sharp eyes, "
"big moustache. Bet he knows more about the charges."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que se refiere al granero al oeste de aquí. Hay otro civil. Ojos "
"penetrantes, bigote grande. Apuesto a que sabe más sobre los cargos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_06"
msgid ""
"You're Dominique? Moustache down to Marseilie, eyes like falcon? Yeah, you "
"match the description."
msgstr ""
"¿Eres Dominique? ¿Bigote hasta Marsella, ojos de halcón? Sí, coincides con "
"la descripción."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_07"
msgid "Oui, je suis Dominique! You are… Des soldats anglais, yes?"
msgstr "¡Sí, soy Dominique! Vosotros sois... soldados ingleses, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_08"
msgid "Monsieur, where did they take the ammo? We need the German explosives."
msgstr ""
"Señor, ¿dónde han llevado la munición? Necesitamos los explosivos alemanes."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_09"
msgid ""
"When you, les Anglais, you come and make noise, ze Boches, zey move ze ammo, "
"oui? They take it... How you say... Plus loin, more far. Suivez-moi? Moi "
"show you!"
msgstr ""
"Cuando vosotros, los ingleses, venís y hacéis ruido, los boches mueven las "
"municiones, ¿oui? Las llevan... ¿Cómo se dice? Plus loin, más lejos. ¿Me "
"seguís? ¡Os lo mostraré!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_10"
msgid "But écoutez, if ze soldats allemands are here… You shoot, d’accord?"
msgstr ""
"Pero escucha, si los soldados alemanes están aquí... Dispara, ¿de acuerdo?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_11"
msgid ""
"Clear out Germans by that barn, and he'll show us where they stashed the "
"charges."
msgstr ""
"Acabad con los alemanes que hay junto al granero y él os dirá dónde han "
"escondido las cargas explosivas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/civilians_12"
msgid "Ça semble sûr maintenant. Come on, go with me!"
msgstr "Ahora parece seguro. ¡Vamos, ven conmigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_01"
msgid ""
"The Germans will be here even sooner than you think. Set up defensive "
"positions. Don’t let them come too close to the bridge. We do not have "
"enough manpower to attack this riverside one more time."
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes llegarán antes de lo que pensás. Prepará posiciones defensivas. "
"No les dejes acercarse demasiado al puente. No tenemos suficientes efectivos "
"para atacar esta ribera una vez más."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_02"
msgid "They're here! Hold the line and keep them off the bridge!"
msgstr "¡Ya están aquí! ¡Mantén la línea y no dejéis que crucen el puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_03"
msgid ""
"I’m trying to raise sections from the other landing zones. They might be "
"able to support us. Hold tight until then."
msgstr ""
"Estoy intentando reunir a secciones de otras zonas de aterrizaje. Quizás "
"puedan ayudarnos. Aguanta hasta entonces."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_04"
msgid "We did it, they’re pulling back!"
msgstr "¡Lo hemos conseguido, se están retirando!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_btr_spawned"
msgid "Heads up, a half-track incoming!"
msgstr "¡Atención, se acerca un semioruga!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_btr_destroyed"
msgid "Good, the half-track is sorted."
msgstr "Bien, el semioruga está arreglado."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_armor_t1_spawned"
msgid ""
"Another one rollin' in! Get the PIAT! And if you’re out, find grenades or "
"something, quick!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya viene otro! ¡Traed el PIAT! Y si no lo tenéis, buscad granadas o algo, "
"¡rápido!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_armor_t1_destroyed"
msgid "Well done, that'll make 'em think twice before pushing again."
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho, eso les hará pensárselo dos veces antes de volver a empujar."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_ammo_out_01"
msgid "I'm dry! I need a fresh mag!"
msgstr "¡Estoy seco! ¡Necesito una revista nueva!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part03_ammo_out_02"
msgid ""
"We are running out of ammunition. Take a look around, you'll probably find "
"some weapon crates left by the Germans."
msgstr ""
"Nos estamos quedando sin municiones. Echa un vistazo a tu alrededor, "
"probablemente encontrarás algunas cajas de armas que dejaron los alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_pl_reinf"
msgid ""
"A squad from another landing zone has arrived. We’ve expected the ground "
"forces but they will work for now too. I reckon they’ve just increased our "
"chances of holding this bridge."
msgstr ""
"Ha llegado un escuadrón de otra zona de aterrizaje. Esperábamos a las "
"fuerzas terrestres, pero por ahora también servirán. Creo que acaban de "
"aumentar nuestras posibilidades de mantener este puente."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_preparation"
msgid ""
"Grab any ammo you can. Search the crates, buildings… Bodies… The Germans "
"could hit us any minute."
msgstr ""
"Coge toda la munición que puedas. Busca en las cajas, en los edificios... en "
"los cadáveres... Los alemanes pueden atacarnos en cualquier momento."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/"
"part04_mortars_offmap_started"
msgid "Incoming mortar! Get to cover!"
msgstr "¡Mortero entrante! ¡Ponte a cubierto!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_mortars_offmap_done"
msgid "They’ve stopped shooting. Means they’re on the move. Get ready, lads!"
msgstr ""
"Han dejado de disparar. Eso significa que se están moviendo. ¡Preparaos, "
"muchachos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_mortar_on_pos"
msgid ""
"They’ve deployed a mortar to the northwest of us! Get rid of it before it "
"buries all of us under this damn bridge!"
msgstr ""
"¡Han desplegado un mortero al noroeste de nosotros! ¡Eliminadlo antes de que "
"nos entierre a todos bajo este maldito puente!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_attack_south_01"
msgid ""
"The Germans are moving in from the south! Make sure this flank is secured, "
"don’t let them surround us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes se acercan por el sur! ¡Asegura este flanco, no dejes que nos "
"rodeen!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_attack_north_01"
msgid ""
"They’re pushing in from the north! Bloody hell, if they break through, that "
"squad of ours and the entire flank are in real trouble!"
msgstr ""
"¡Están avanzando desde el norte! ¡Maldita sea, si logran atravesar nuestras "
"líneas, nuestro escuadrón y todo el flanco estarán en serios problemas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_at_on_position"
msgid "Eyes on the western direction, lads! They’ve brought in an AT gun."
msgstr "¡Mirad hacia el oeste, muchachos! Han traído un cañón antitanque."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/part04_commandos_arrived"
msgid ""
"Just look who finally decided to show up! Commandos! These guys are as tough "
"as they come. Now it's Jerry who's got the problem. Let's destroy the "
"remaining attacking forces together."
msgstr ""
"¡Mirad quién ha decidido aparecer por fin! ¡Los comandos! Estos tipos son "
"muy duros. Ahora son los boches quienes tienen un problema. Destruyamos "
"juntos las fuerzas atacantes que quedan."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/bridge_captured"
msgid "We lost the Bridge! Get over there and take it back, now!"
msgstr "¡Hemos perdido el puente! ¡Id allí y recuperadlo, ahora mismo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/bridge_recaptured"
msgid "Good, the bridge is ours again. I nearly got a heart attack."
msgstr "Bien, el puente vuelve a ser nuestro. Casi me da un infarto."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/b33r"
msgid "Quenching thirst at work? Since when have you become Irish?"
msgstr "¿Saciar la sed en el trabajo? ¿Desde cuándo te has vuelto irlandés?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cafe"
msgid ""
"Café Goon… Goon-dry? Christ, sounds like something you catch, not drink. Ah, "
"Gondrée. Bloody French."
msgstr ""
"Café Goon... ¿Goon-dry? Dios, suena como algo que se pilla, no como algo que "
"se bebe. Ah, Gondrée. Malditos franceses."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/ushanka"
msgid ""
"Have the Soviets really got such hats? No way they are seriously wearing "
"furry rotten teabags on their heads."
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad los soviéticos tienen esos sombreros? No es posible que lleven en "
"serio bolsas de té podridas y peludas en la cabeza."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_01"
msgid ""
"You’re telling me they are so late because were dragging the damn "
"orchestra?.."
msgstr ""
"¿Me estás diciendo que llegan tan tarde porque estaban retrasando a la "
"maldita orquesta?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_02"
msgid ""
"Gentlemen, frightfully sorry for the terrible delay. Traffic on the beaches "
"was nothing short of murderous."
msgstr ""
"Señores, lamento muchísimo el terrible retraso. El tráfico en las playas era "
"sencillamente infernal."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_03"
msgid ""
"Great to see you here, your lordship. We managed so far, but now we’re at "
"the end of our tether to be honest."
msgstr ""
"Me alegro de verte aquí, señor. Hasta ahora nos las hemos arreglado, pero "
"ahora estamos al límite, para ser sinceros."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_04"
msgid ""
"You have held this sector with remarkable resolve. An exceptional "
"achievement indeed. I shall raise the matter of your promotion with Command. "
"They already owe you a proper drink, preferably something French."
msgstr ""
"Has mantenido este sector con una determinación extraordinaria. Sin duda, un "
"logro excepcional. Plantearé tu ascenso al mando. Ya te deben una copa, "
"preferiblemente algo francés."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_05"
msgid ""
"We’ll agree to anything spirit-based, your lordship. Even if it tastes like "
"petrol."
msgstr ""
"Aceptaremos cualquier cosa que contenga alcohol, señor. Aunque sepa a "
"gasolina."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_06"
msgid ""
"But you sound dreadfully weary, gentlemen. To your good fortune, we brought "
"some sleeping bags. Have a rest chaps, before sheer exhaustion claims you."
msgstr ""
"Pero parecéis terriblemente cansados, caballeros. Por suerte para vosotros, "
"hemos traído unos sacos de dormir. Descansad un poco, muchachos, antes de "
"que el agotamiento os venza."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_07"
msgid ""
"I reckon that’s even better than a wine. And my back… It’s so numb. Thank "
"you, Milord."
msgstr ""
"Creo que eso es incluso mejor que un vino. Y mi espalda... Está tan "
"entumecida. Gracias, Milord."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/narrator/cutscene/outro_08"
msgid "I shan’t trouble you any longer. Worry not, we’ll take care of it."
msgstr "No te molestaré más. No te preocupes, nosotros nos encargaremos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/tasks/01_clear"
msgid "Take control of the Bénouville bridge"
msgstr "Toma el control del puente de Bénouville."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/tasks/02_explosives"
msgid "Find and neutralize the demolition charges"
msgstr "Encuentra y neutraliza los explosivos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/tasks/04_flak38"
msgid "Destroy the 20mm anti-air gun"
msgstr "Destruye el cañón antiaéreo de 20 mm."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/tasks/05_bridge_night"
msgid "Defeat the enemy counterattack"
msgstr "Derrota el contraataque enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_06_05_pegasus/tasks/06_bridge_morning"
msgid "Hold the bridge until relieved"
msgstr "Mantén el puente hasta que te releven."

